\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa95\li540\fi-270\bullet\tab The same logical coordinate must identify the same effective weight before and after qkv packing or unpacking.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa95\li540\fi-270\bullet\tab Head-aware vectorisation, CUDA kernel layout, activation-checkpoint segmentation and materialisation order must not alter the address.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa95\li540\fi-270\bullet\tab A one-code mutation test must demonstrate that exactly one intended matrix element changes.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa95\li540\fi-270\bullet\tab Checkpoint loading must validate every tensor key and matrix shape before accepting stored remainder values.\par
