\pard\ql\f1\fs25\sb160\sa100\cf1\keepn\b 7.1  Required dtype order\b0\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa100\li540\fi-360 1. Materialise the base weight through the existing THOG2 path.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa100\li540\fi-360 2. Cast a detached copy to the resolved effective dtype for decoding.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa100\li540\fi-360 3. Decode the remainder in that dtype.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa100\li540\fi-360 4. Cast the decoded result to the carrier dtype used by the straight-through expression.\par
\pard\ql\f0\fs22\sb0\sa100\li540\fi-360 5. Allow the existing operation and autocast path to perform the final execution casts.\par
